<i>♪ Que será. será ♪</i>

47
00:02:54.800 --> 00:02:57.602
<i>♪ What will be. will be ♪</i>

48
00:03:06.932 --> 00:03:11.417
<i>♪ Now I have children</i>
<i>Of my own ♪</i>

49
00:03:11.857 --> 00:03:16.622
<i>♪ They ask their father</i>
<i>"What will I be?" ♪</i>

50
